      "author": "github-actions[bot]",
      "description": "* Use sentence case for all UI strings.\r\n* Replace `.setName(...)` and `createEl(..., { text })` with sentence case labels.\r\n* Avoid using the word \"settings\" in section headers.\r\n* Use `.setHeading()` for section headers instead of `createEl('h6', ...)`.\r\n* Use `app.saveLocalStorage` and `app.loadLocalStorage` instead of `localStorage.setItem` / `getItem`.\r\n* Avoid using `localStorage.clear()` as it removes all data across vaults.\r\n* Clean up injected CSS when it's no longer needed.\r\n* Assign unique IDs to `<style>` elements and remove them on unmount or update.\r\n* Do not pass the plugin instance to `MarkdownRenderer.render(...)`.\r\n* Use a short-lived `Component` in `MarkdownRenderer.render(...)` and call `.unload()` when done.",
